menu "breadboard: bb_ota_pull"

config BB_OTA_PULL_AUTOREGISTER
    bool "Auto-register OTA pull HTTP routes via bb_registry"
    default y
    help
        When enabled, bb_ota_pull self-registers its HTTP route handlers
        through bb_registry. Disable this if you want to keep bb_ota_pull's
        public C API but drive route registration manually or skip routes
        entirely (e.g. headless OTA-driver use).

endmenu
